OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinister considering       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbackdating jail cost rules 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The justice secretary said he was      
OL,6, considering backdating new rules which 
OL,7, mean wrongly convicted people will no  
OL,8, longer have prison living costs        
OL,9, deducted from compensation.            
OL,11,FAlex Chalk said he was looking into    
OL,12,Fthree cases "very carefully" after the 
OL,13,Frule was scrapped.                     
OL,15,FIt comes after Andrew Malkinson, who   
OL,16,Fspent 17 years in jail for a rape he   
OL,17,Fdid not commit, was cleared.           
OL,19,FMr Chalk his "blood ran cold" when he  
OL,20,Fheard about what had happened.         
